Looking for $900 or best offer. I think this is a very fair price compared to other mini-14's that I've seen.

After speaking with someone from FN, more information has come to light about this particular Hi Power, and my earlier information was deemed incorrect.

This pistol is from one of the first production runs out of FN after Liege was liberated from the Germans, assembled from parts produced under German occupation but with all Liege/Allied markings (no German stamping of any sort).
